<!--
  Simple Humanoid Robot URDF

  This URDF defines a basic humanoid robot with:
  - Torso (base)
  - Head
  - Two arms (shoulder, elbow, wrist)
  - Two legs (hip, knee, ankle)

  All dimensions are approximate for educational purposes.
-->
<robot name="simple_humanoid">

